        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "1. Artificial Intelligence: Beyond the Hype"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "AI has moved from science fiction to everyday reality. Tools like ChatGPT, Midjourney, and autonomous vehicles are just the beginning. But as AI grows more powerful, so do the ethical concerns:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "attrs": {
          "tight": false
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Job Disruption"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Will AI replace human roles, or will it create new opportunities?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Bias & Fairness"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": How do we ensure AI models don’t perpetuate harmful stereotypes?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Regulation"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Should governments impose strict controls on AI development?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Despite these challenges, AI’s potential for healthcare, education, and scientific discovery is immense. The key lies in responsible innovation."
